Class BTAlgorithmInterested

java.lang.Object
  de.tud.kom.p2psim.overlay.bt.algorithm.BTAlgorithmInterested
All Implemented Interfaces:
BTAlgorithm
public class BTAlgorithmInterested
extends java.lang.Object
implements BTAlgorithm

This class calculates the interest of a peer in the other peers data. If they have data that we don't have, we are interested.

Author:
Jan Stolzenburg
